[What is not clear in this report is whether these individuals are among the original group tested or potentially have later dates of onset of symptoms. If the latter, the date of lifting the quarantine will be extended from the 19 Feb 2020 date. It is also not clear if these 5 crew members had regular contact with passengers or if they were separate from passengers due to the type of jobs they had. We await more information on this continuing unfolding situation. - Mod.MPP]

