[This event highlights the ease of global travel for the virus. It started in China, and there is now local transmission ongoing in Singapore. A UK citizen stopped off in France en route to the UK from Singapore, and visited with family (? and friends) in France; some returned to Majorca, Spain (where they presumably live), with others returning to the UK. With all of this travel, one has to remember the airplane flights and airports. - Mod.MPP]

